sequenceDiagram
    participant Runtime as Agent Runtime
    participant Protocol as Agent Protocol
    participant PR as Protocol Runtime
    participant Identity as Identity / Handle Validation
    participant Policy as Permission Engine
    participant Scheduler
    participant Sandbox
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Note over Runtime,Audit: Critical Path: 6 steps, ALL must complete before result returned

    Runtime->>Protocol: ① invoke(action)
    Protocol->>PR: normalized request
    
    Note right of PR: Step 1: Identity Validation
    PR->>Identity: validate handle
    Identity-->>PR: valid
    
    Note right of PR: Step 2: Capability Check
    PR->>Policy: evaluate capabilities
    Policy-->>PR: permitted
    
    Note right of PR: Step 3: Resource Scheduling
    PR->>Scheduler: reserve / enqueue
    Scheduler-->>PR: slot granted
    
    Note right of PR: Step 4: Isolated Execution
    PR->>Sandbox: execute action
    Sandbox-->>PR: action result
    
    Note right of PR: Step 5: Audit WAL Write (CRITICAL)
    rect rgb(255, 238, 221)
        PR->>Audit: append WAL entry
        Note right of Audit: Must be durable before result observable
        Audit-->>PR: durable write complete
    end
    
    Note right of PR: Step 6: Return Result
    PR-->>Runtime: ActionResult
    
    Note over Runtime,Audit: Invariant: Result NOT observable until Step 5 completes
